videos.headline: Fan proposes in the pouring rain
videos.description: During the Miami-Duke game, a couple gets engaged in the downpour.

videos.headline: Miami RB rips off 83-yard TD run
videos.description: DeeJay Dallas sprints up the middle and outraces Duke defenders for an 83-yard touchdown in the pouring rain.

videos.headline: Miami DB tips ball to himself for INT
videos.description: Daniel Jones' throw bounces off the chest of a Duke WR and Jaquan Johnson reaches up to tip the ball to himself for a Miami interception.
